  "texts": [
    "However, relying on manually extracted low-level features for segmentation tasks makes it difficult to handle complex scenarios and does not effectively utilize global contextual information [7].In recent years, deep learning-based polyp segmentation models have demonstrated impressive capabilities in locating and segmenting polyp regions.",
    "Based on the encoderdecoder architecture, some works focus on enhancing the output features of the encoder [8,9].",
    "In addition, the variation between datasets collected from different devices is also an issue [10].",
    "After the emergence of the segment anything model (SAM) [11], fine-grained models based on universal segmentation networks have shown promising momentum in polyp segmentation [12].",
    "To provide a Figure 1 A brief chronology of polyp segmentation."
  ]
